    <p class="section-number">Scope</p>
    <h2>What we do for commercial slicers, and what we don't.</h2>

    <p><strong>We service:</strong> Hobart HS-series gravity-feed slicers, Globe slicers, Bizerba premium slicers, Berkel modern and vintage. Blade sharpening (on-site honing plus full sharpening), blade replacement (NSF-listed OEM), safety interlock service (OSHA compliance), blade guard replacement, motor replacement, sharpener stone replacement, drive belt, food carriage rebuild, complete sanitization-compliant repair documentation.</p>

    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> blade sharpening service truck only (we do on-site work, not separate sharpening route service); high-speed automatic slicers for industrial production lines (specialty industrial trade); slicer training certification (OSHA-required operator training is a separate certification track). New slicer installation we coordinate but don't perform; specialty installer trade for cabinet integration and electrical drops.</p>
